text: Learn — Find Sellers Home Seller Types Retiree Landlord Deferred Maintenance FAQ Learn Pricing FAQ Login Home Seller Types Retiree Landlord Deferred Maintenance FAQ Learn Pricing FAQ Login Intelligent Direct Marketing Lists Your prospecting list is the most important component of any direct marketing Get your message in front of the right property owner, and you’ve already won half the Send your message to the wrong people, and your response rates will suffer So who are the “right property owners?” Cue predictive analytics! How Predictive Analytics Increases Response Rates Predictive analytics, or more broadly, Artificial Intelligence, can help us identify which property owners are most likely to sell in a given Advances in machine learning and artificial intelligence have enabled us to analyze vast amounts of property, financial, and demographic data in order to observe trends among current Broadly speaking, predictive analytics looks at patterns in data and assigns a predictive score based on some outcome of In our case, this outcome is whether or not a property owner is likely to Using predictive analytics, both real estate agents and investors alike can create a prospecting list to maximize response rates on a direct marketing But what exactly is direct marketing you may ask? Opposed to putting up a billboard or sending a radio blast to a wide audience, direct marketing is a marketing strategy where you directly target the individual of In real estate, often takes the form of mailing a postcard or , , or a property owner in your prospecting In real estate , predictive analytics can help you reach the right audience by giving you more control over who receives your With the ability to segment your list by demographic data and , targeted direct marketing can increase traditional response rates from less than 1% to over %, saving you money on your overall cost of mailing while generating more leads for your real estate We Make Targeted Direct Marketing Easy Pulling off a successful targeted campaign is no easy Thankfully, Find Sellers has simplified the lead generation process by developing a predictive algorithm that ranks each property owner given their current propensity to Real estate investors can use our Distressed Score , which predicts the likelihood of the property owner selling % or more below current market value, and real estate agents use our Conventional Seller Score , which predicts the likelihood of the property owner selling at full market We also provide proprietary search filters to narrow down your list by owner demographics and property characteristics, allowing users to craft their prospecting letter to a specific audience and increase response rates on , , and campaigns across the Visit to generate your intelligent direct marketing list and become more efficient and effective in your lead generation With daily updates, you can be confident that you’re targeting the right property owners whenever you decide to send your next mailer, make your next , or go out At $49 mo for unlimited seller prospecting lists, Find Sellers is a cost effective tool to increase response rates on your next campaign, Home Seller Trends by Zip Code October - There’s no pressure! In today’s world of “Think big, start small, and scale or fail fast,” having a business deck or one pager explaining your business idea, growth strategy, or plan to pivot is vital to communicate with your team, employees, and most importantly, potential customers and But, the limits of time and financial resources prevent you from doing it yourself, or outsourcing to This is why we created We are here to provide you with the business deck, elevator pitch, or consulting needs you seek without constraining your time or your Our flagship product, the DeckLaunch Package is created to provide you with a road map to your business future, and a means to connect to professional organizations that can help you take the next step you’ve been waiting It’s never too early or too late to set your plan in Why not launch it? HOW TO DECK LAUNCH Apply on our site and share your story with our We match you with a consultant based on your industry, need, and scope of your pitch We develop a two week plan for your pitch deck, FAQ — Street FC 0 Skip to Content Rules FAQ Shop Open Menu Close Menu Rules FAQ Shop Open Menu Close Menu Rules FAQ Shop What is Street FC? Street FC is building the biggest football club on the We host street soccer games on surfaces in cities around the USA, and we’re assembling a giant community full of players and Our game format is designed to make soccer accessible to as many people as possible – providing a level playing field for men and women, girls and boys, and people of all ages and skill The Street FC app is core to the experience and it allows players to book into games, helps to manage players of different skill levels, and works to connect our community of players online and in the real What are Street FC games like? Street FC games are street soccer games played on hard Players book into minute “sessions” and we play as many 4 minute “games” as we can in each 1 hour Each session has players, each game is (three teams total), with a “winner stays” format deciding who gets to play We keep score, but not And, we are constantly switching up the teams to keep the play You can learn more from reading our rules . Is Street FC in my city? We aspire to bring Street FC to cities around the US and around the We’re currently live in NYC NJ, Boston, Philly, Baltimore, Atlanta, Minneapolis, Austin, Denver, Las Vegas, Los Angeles and San If you would like to bring Street FC to your city, please let us Before we launch in a city, we do try to find an amazing place where we can play , so if you’ve seen great courts or in your neighborhood, let us Why only hard surfaces and games? We are focused on making soccer as accessible as possible to as many people as That means playing on spaces in cities (where concrete is easy to find, while grass and turf are not) and leveling the playing field to make speed and strength less important to be Small sided games on hard surfaces accomplish What skill level do I have to be to play? Depending on the city you’re in, you can be of any skill level to enjoy playing in a Street FC In some cities, we currently host games for Beginners, Intermediate, and Advanced We also aspire to offer games for people who have never played before and for youth players of all levels and If your skill level doesn’t match any of the games we are offering, please let us know . How do I get into a game? Download the Street FC app to get Our weekly game schedule drops on Sunday night, and we allow players to book games up to 8 days in Our games fill up fast, so make sure to have the Street FC app handy when new games are about to If you miss out, you can always join a game’s “waitlist” (and as a waitlist grows, we often spawn new games and send a notification to those who may want to join). What should I bring to a game? We bring all the gear (goals, balls, pinnies), so all you need to do is bring clothes to play in and some shoes (no cleats, no spikes). Bring some water and a good attitude too! What happens if I can’t make it? If you can’t make it, no We just ask that you give our community enough time to fill your spot (our games are most fun when all spots are filled!). You can read more about our cancelation policy here [insert link]. How much does Street FC cost? When you join Street FC, your first game is After that, players choose to become Street FC Members ($35 month) to play in unlimited games or purchase “Guest Passes” for $10 game. When you become a Street FC member, you receive full access to the Street FC community including our Discord chat server , merch drops, invites to events and watch parties, and other exclusive perks and Free Guess Passes are also available to players who refer their friends to download our app and and play in Street FC How do I get a refund? If your game is canceled because of weather or other unforeseen circumstances, you will automatically be refunded your Guest In the event you’d like a refund for other reasons, please contact us . How old do I have to be to play? Our games are currently meant for adults (18+) although we often make exceptions to skilled players (15 and up). You can reach out to us directly if you’re over and would like to play in a match (as we may need written consent from your parent or guardian). How can I get involved? How can I host games? We’re always looking for “Game Captains” to help us host more Street FC games and bring Street FC to more We pay our Game Captains a for hosting games (a gig that includes greeting players, recruiting players, bringing gear to games, and set up and clean up). If you’d like to learn more, please reach out . What does a Street FC court look like? The ideal court is about the size of a basketball court (100 feet long x feet wide) with a that is not slick (concrete and asphalt are great, sealed concrete and SportCourt™ surfaces are less great). The court itself should have good ball retention (with a fence or wall surrounding it), and be in a safe and area with good Don’t worry if the space doesn’t

Memberships & Programs Gym Membership Membership Pricing Panda Programmer Calendar and Events Calendar and Classes FLEX Birthdays Camps News Videos Contact Contact Careers Searching for a CSGO Coach Home Entertainment Searching for a CSGO Coach January , admin Entertainment Part Time – Head CSGO Coach We are looking for a CSGO coach to help our high school age members take their game to the next This coach has a solid understanding of the game’s skills and meta and knows how to work well and motivate their Coaches are the lifeblood of The Game They are not simply coaches, they are community mentors and The goal of a Game Gym coach is not to produce “the best gamers,” but to provide an experience where all members can grow and learn at their own On a regular day, a Game Gym coach will lead one or more group lessons in the game of their During the lesson, the coach will explain and demonstrate the lesson and skill of the day and lead scrimmages and training Coaches will also be expected to guide their groups through competitions and end year Responsibilities Coach group lessons Assist in tournament organizing Be available for private lessons Requirements Must work well with gamers age Deep understanding of game mechanics and strategies Experience working with camps and other youth programs Willingness to learn how to coach other games Willingness to become CPR and First Aid certified Excellent communication organizational skills Must work well with others and handle a environment Passage of a background check To apply, please send a resume and cover letter to 0 comments Share Spring Season Kick Off Panda Programmer Comments are Categories Entertainment Esports Newsletter To stay up to date on all the Game Gym news, sign up for our monthly newsletter! This enables them to manage the investment more efficiently Greater Transparency + More Access to Companies Capital providers have , direct communication with companies and management personnel through working through firms such as Bassett Creek that are involved in direct investments in certain Private equity, on the other hand, often view their investments as one of many in a While Bassett Creek works with private equity, it provides an extra layer of expertise, both financial and operational, and further provides direct communication between their private equity partners and management of the Higher Returns Direct investments offer many advantages to all parties concerned, private equity investors, other capital providers, sellers, as well as, management Quality Over Quantity Traditional PE firms face pressure to put all of the “committed” capital to work, thereby creating an incentive to focus on quantity of deals rather than quality The incentive for direct investments, on the other hand, is on quality investments as capital is only allocated to specific, identified Copyright Bassett Creek Capital,   Team — Bassett Creek Capital Bassett Creek Capital Investment Philosophy Why Bassett Creek? Protect Your Reputation Cybersecurity Blue Team Cybersecurity Blue Team Cybersecurity Blue Team Services Overview Lockard offers a robust offensive and defensive cybersecurity These services are known as Red Team Blue Team On this page, we’re going to talk about our defensive cybersecurity services known as the Blue We get asked what is the difference between our cybersecurity red team vs blue team We’re excited to answer this question along with any others you may Click the Red Team link to learn more about Lockard’s Red Team Cybersecurity services and check out what Wikipedia Our Cybersecurity Blue Team Services is a mix of the following people, processes and Our folks are industry certified experts with backgrounds in cybersecurity architecture and engineering, penetration testing, incident handling and response, malware analysis, threat intelligence and threat The technology we leverage includes what we recommend and use, to supporting what technology our customers may Our tactics, techniques and processes are crafted from years of experience from working in Fortune companies, government agencies along with the Capabilities Lockard’s Cybersecurity Blue Team Service allows us to provide x 7 x coverage leveraging our experienced certified We keep eyes on screens, hands on keyboards and ears and ready to answer calls or jump on conference With our team of experts, they’ll be monitoring, alerting and responding to incidents in real Depending on the needs of your company, you can either leverage Lockard’s Cybersecurity Blue Team as your entire Information Security (InfoSec) Otherwise we can work closely together with your existing InfoSec team as Our team will create run books, identify gaps and make recommendations where Blue Team Tools – SIEM In order for an Information Security organization to be successful requires more than just head count, it also requires The main Blue Team Toolkit is what’s known as a Security Information and Event Management (SIEM). A SIEM is an extremely important tool in the arsenal as it provides organizations with detection, analytics and response SIEM’s leverage advanced rule correlation paired with machine learning to alert on known bad and suspicious patterns of SIEM architecture can get fairly complex and complicated depending on the companies For Lockard to be successful will require having a Due to the extreme costs of buying and running a SIEM, we realize not all companies have That is why Lockard will include a SIEM if you don’t have If you already have a SIEM, Lockard will work with Our experts will tune SIEM rules to improve signal to noise ratios, investigate alerts and drive incident response efforts to Lockard experts will provide recommendations and suggestions to improve operations, meet any compliance needs and troubleshoot issues that may SIEM’s are a living thing that keeps growing and Ensuring all of the requirements are being met to take full advantage of the SIEM like having log data, net flow, EDR integration along with some more advance features like Security Orchestration and Response (SOAR). Otherwise Lockard will work with our SIEM and integrate it into your companies Eco Blue Team Tools – SOAR Once the SIEM has been tuned and running very smoothly for a period of time, the next logical step is to build in additional automation Generally speaking this is referred to as Security Orchestration, Automation and Response (SOAR). The SOAR technology helps coordinate, execute and automate tasks between various people and tools typically referred to as run To take full advantage of SOAR requires to have a complete Eco system of Security tools that all work together and support integrations between each Most commonly we see prebuild connectors between security tools is the easiest way to accomplish this More advanced integrations leverage API’s and or other Additionally SSHing and or Remote PowerShell can be used to trigger scripts and other tasks as defined in said run Typically SOAR is a long term goal for organizations to get What makes it so challenging is the risks of false positives interrupting business Taking down production systems can have a detrimental impact on a companies bottom line so its important to slowly rollout SOAR capabilities to high confident levels of assurance on Most companies require run book validation, auditing and tracking changes, along with extensive testing prior to a production SOAR requires Security Engineers that understand code and can write and troubleshoot it as Otherwise companies will not get the full benefit of the SOAR This is where

Blog - Venus Media Group About Capabilities Blog Contact International Women’s Day Having been raised in a multicultural, Colombian and Irish, home, I am thankful that I can raise my daughter in a world where multiculturalism is no longer taboo, but welcomed! Multicultural homes are growing by leaps and bounds, and schools with or more languages represented are becoming the As a multicultural mom raising a multicultural daughter, I believe that children who grow up within cultural diversity are more likely to learn that the world is a big place at a young age: they understand that people speak different languages because often their own family members do, they may worship differently, they are likely to eat more varied foods… and the list goes on and Plus, school becomes more interactive learning geography is no longer something you read about in a textbook, it’s a world view they may have experienced These experiences and this knowledge provides emotional benefits, allowing kids to feel more confident about the world around Being a mom to a multicultural daughter has taught me many lessons! International Women’s Day is one day we love to celebrate here at Venus Media Group!
